in their way.

41:29.400 --> 41:32.200
You bloody well
leave us out of this.

41:32.200 --> 41:34.240
At least we've got some decency.

41:34.280 --> 41:36.200
What do you think
you're doing...

41:36.200 --> 41:39.080
