01:37:57.280 --> 01:37:58.840
He did...

01:37:58.880 --> 01:38:00.680
until I remembered you.

01:38:02.640 --> 01:38:04.200
Touché.

01:38:05.080 --> 01:38:06.920
What are you doing back here?

01:38:06.960 --> 01:38:09.680
Just visiting.
I heard about your misfortune...

01:38:09.720 --> 01:38:12.280
thought I'd see
if you needed anything.

01:38:12.320 --> 01:38:15.160
You know what I really need,
baby?

01:38:15.200 --> 01:38:18.040
I need you to stay out
of my life.

01:38:18.080 --> 01:38:21.080
You haven't lost your charm,
Oscar. I should have known.

01:38:21.120 --> 01:38:25.080
Well... good-bye.

01:38:37.360 --> 01:38:39.280
Remember the carousel?

01:38:39.360 --> 01:38:41.240
Sure, I remember the carousel.

01:38:41.280 --> 01:38:44.440
I remember it
like a trip to the dentist.

01:38:44.480 --> 01:38:46.440
Easy! Easy!

01:38:46.480 --> 01:38:48.000
Stop!

01:38:52.680 --> 01:38:55.680
Asshole.
Did you think I'd forgotten?

01:39:10.160 --> 01:39:13.200
She came to see me when
I got out of intensive care.

01:39:13.240 --> 01:39:15.480
She said, "There's bad news
and there's good news.

01:39:15.520 --> 01:39:19.000
"You're paralyzed from
the waist down, permanently."

01:39:19.040 --> 01:39:20.760
"OK," I said.

01:39:20.800 --> 01:39:22.280
"Let's have the good news."

01:39:22.320 --> 01:39:25.640
"That was the good news,"
she said.

01:39:25.680 --> 01:39:28.280
"The bad news
is that from now on...

01:39:28.320 --> 01:39:30.200
"I'm taking care of you."

01:39:35.440 --> 01:39:38.160
We were a couple once more.

01:39:38.200 --> 01:39:41.120
She moved back into my place
and looked after me...

01:39:41.160 --> 01:39:43.840
with a strange kind of devotion
to duty.

01:39:43.880 --> 01:39:47.800
She was my cook,
my housekeeper, my jailer...

01:39:47.840 --> 01:39:50.040
and my nurse.

01:39:57.600 --> 01:39:59.480
Oh, couldn't you...

01:39:59.520 --> 01:40:01.520
I mean, it makes my leg shake...

01:40:01.560 --> 01:40:05.080
if you always shoot me
in the same spot.

01:40:05.120 --> 01:40:07.920
You see? It makes the leg shake.

01:40:07.960 --> 01:40:10.200
Couldn't you find
some other place?

01:40:10.240 --> 01:40:13.560
- You want me to have another go?
- No, the next time.

01:40:13.600 --> 01:40:16.000
Look what you made me do, silly.

01:40:23.400 --> 01:40:25.720
My God, you're not
going to use it again?

01:40:25.760 --> 01:40:27.480
None left.

01:40:27.520 --> 01:40:29.040
I'll get some more tomorrow.

01:40:33.280 --> 01:40:37.560
It crossed my mind
she might still love me...

01:40:37.600 --> 01:40:39.840
in spite of everything.

01:40:39.880 --> 01:40:42.440
After all, it's no fun
hurting someone...

01:40:42.480 --> 01:40:44.800
who means nothing to you.

01:40:44.840 --> 01:40:47.800
Hey, Tiger. Come and get it.

01:40:56.120 --> 01:40:57.400
Aren't you having any?

01:40:57.440 --> 01:40:58.720
I'm going out.

01:41:02.000 --> 01:41:03.080
Nothing in it?

01:41:03.120 --> 01:41:04.320
Like what?

01:41:04.360 --> 01:41:07.560
I don't know.
Maybe tomatoes, mushrooms?

01:41:07.600 --> 01:41:09.560
Would you like some mushrooms?

01:41:09.600 --> 01:41:11.920
Well, yeah. That would be nice.

01:41:12.880 --> 01:41:15.040
You want some, go pick some.

01:41:20.480 --> 01:41:21.880
Yes, I do.

01:41:23.400 --> 01:41:25.400
Oh, no, he's not available.

01:41:25.440 --> 01:41:27.160
Who's calling, please?

01:41:31.640 --> 01:41:34.480
No. This is his nurse speaking.

01:41:34.520 --> 01:41:36.880
What the...
Who says I'm not available?

01:41:38.200 --> 01:41:40.400
Ah, you heard.

01:41:41.360 --> 01:41:43.120
Yeah, very sad.

01:41:45.120 --> 01:41:46.360
Who is it?

01:41:48.080 --> 01:41:50.200
No. Quite impossible,
I'm afraid.

01:41:50.240 --> 01:41:52.360
He's completely incapacitated.

01:41:55.200 --> 01:41:56.680
I will.

01:41:56.720 --> 01:41:58.600
You're welcome. Good-bye.

01:41:58.640 --> 01:41:59.800
Who was it?

01:42:00.960 --> 01:42:03.840
"Paris is out. Vieux jeu."

01:42:03.880 --> 01:42:06.320
Beverly, you mean?
What did she want?

01:42:09.000 --> 01:42:11.360
What did she want,
for God's sake?

01:42:11.400 --> 01:42:12.800
How would I know?

01:42:12.840 --> 01:42:15.240
You might have let me
speak to her.

01:42:17.760 --> 01:42:20.120
I said, you might have
let me speak to her.

01:42:20.160 --> 01:42:21.800
I heard you.

01:42:21.840 --> 01:42:27.040
Jesus, Mimi, I never get to see
or speak to a soul these days.

01:42:27.080 --> 01:42:29.200
It's like I'm in solitary.

01:42:29.240 --> 01:42:30.360
Is it?

01:42:33.120 --> 01:42:34.280
Look...

01:42:35.600 --> 01:42:38.000
I know I deserve all I get.

01:42:38.880 --> 01:42:41.240
I treated you like a monster.

01:42:41.280 --> 01:42:42.680
I am a monster.

01:42:42.720 --> 01:42:46.240
Tiger! You don't have the right
to criticize yourself.

01:42:46.280 --> 01:42:48.000
That's my privilege.

01:42:48.040 --> 01:42:50.280
- I know.
- I earned it.

01:42:50.320 --> 01:42:53.360
But I promise,
I will never hurt you again.

01:42:58.400 --> 01:43:00.600
You... hurt me?

01:43:00.640 --> 01:43:01.880
Very funny.

01:43:06.240 --> 01:43:09.240
And don't play with your zizi
while I'm gone.

01:43:09.280 --> 01:43:10.840
There is no point.

01:44:10.480 --> 01:44:12.840
Thank God you're home.

01:44:12.880 --> 01:44:15.160
You missed me?

01:44:15.200 --> 01:44:17.560
As much as you missed me
after you dumped me?

01:44:17.600 --> 01:44:19.160
Oh, no, not that again.

01:44:19.200 --> 01:44:21.400
Please, let's not have a scene.

01:44:21.440 --> 01:44:23.680
Why not? I love scenes.

01:44:23.720 --> 01:44:25.720
I've developed a taste for them.

01:44:25.760 --> 01:44:28.720
In fact,
I can't do without them.

01:44:28.760 --> 01:44:30.440
What is that?

01:44:30.480 --> 01:44:33.240
What do you think it is?

01:44:33.280 --> 01:44:36.720
What do you expect if you go out
and leave me alone all night?

01:44:38.240 --> 01:44:40.120
I wet myself, of course.

01:44:40.160 --> 01:44:41.920
Oh, poor Tiger.

01:44:41.960 --> 01:44:44.000
I'd better change your diaper.

01:44:44.040 --> 01:44:45.560
God, you stink.

01:44:45.600 --> 01:44:48.440
Why don't you
just finish me off?

01:44:48.480 --> 01:44:50.040
Why don't you O. D. Me...

01:44:50.080 --> 01:44:53.120
or push me down the stairs
or something?

01:44:54.760 --> 01:44:56.200
I almost forgot.

01:45:00.800 --> 01:45:02.520
It's your birthday, isn't it?

01:45:05.160 --> 01:45:07.080
Is it?

01:45:07.120 --> 01:45:08.360
I didn't remember.

01:45:46.240 --> 01:45:47.560
Happy birthday to you

01:45:47.600 --> 01:45:48.880
Happy birthday to you

01:45:48.920 --> 01:45:50.200
Happy birthday, dear Oscar

01:45:50.240 --> 01:45:51.360
Happy birthday to you

01:46:11.520 --> 01:46:14.400
Although she kept me
starved of human contact...

01:46:14.400 --> 01:46:16.640
she enjoyed taking me out...

01:46:16.680 --> 01:46:19.320
because she knew how much
it hurt to be reminded...

01:46:19.360 --> 01:46:23.720
of the simple little pleasures
that were denied me forevermore.

01:46:24.960 --> 01:46:27.160
Antoine,
laisse le monsieur tranquille...

01:46:27.200 --> 01:46:29.120
tu vois qu'il a bobo.

01:46:33.000 --> 01:46:35.680
Funny. You might have
been good with kids.

01:46:35.720 --> 01:46:37.320
Who knows?

01:46:37.360 --> 01:46:39.520
You never will.
That's for sure.

01:46:41.360 --> 01:46:44.440
It wasn't that I just didn't
want that child we made.

01:46:44.480 --> 01:46:47.000
I didn't think
I was worthy of it.

01:46:47.040 --> 01:46:49.400
You could still have some.

01:46:49.440 --> 01:46:50.680
No fear of that.

01:46:50.720 --> 01:46:53.160
I'm a safe fuck these days.

01:46:53.200 --> 01:46:54.480
What do you mean?

01:46:56.480 --> 01:46:59.000
That abortion
you so kindly paid for...

01:46:59.040 --> 01:47:01.480
left me with an infection.

01:47:01.520 --> 01:47:03.360
I was quite ill in Martinique.

01:47:03.400 --> 01:47:06.520
Almost died,
as a matter of fact.

01:47:06.560 --> 01:47:08.480
You never told me.

01:47:08.480 --> 01:47:10.880
Well, I'm telling you now.

01:47:10.920 --> 01:47:14.640
Oh, Christ, what a shit I was.
I despise myself.

01:47:14.680 --> 01:47:16.080
I hate myself.

01:47:16.160 --> 01:47:19.000
I hate myself worse
than you could ever hate me.

01:47:19.040 --> 01:47:20.720
Don't kid yourself, Oscar.

01:47:20.760 --> 01:47:23.600
No one could hate you
more than I do.

01:47:28.480 --> 01:47:30.640
Why do you stay with me?

01:47:30.680 --> 01:47:32.400
You really don't know?

01:47:32.440 --> 01:47:37.640
Because you're precious to me,
more precious than ever before.

01:47:37.680 --> 01:47:38.960
Here.

01:47:39.000 --> 01:47:40.400
So there it was.

01:47:40.440 --> 01:47:43.400
We needed each other, she and I.

01:47:45.400 --> 01:47:47.280
It's getting awfully cold.

01:47:49.760 --> 01:47:51.960
Mimi, the water's getting cold.

01:47:53.080 --> 01:47:56.440
Oh, merde.
It's run out again.

01:47:56.480 --> 01:47:58.680
I must speak to the concierge
about it.

01:48:00.320 --> 01:48:01.720
Don't go away.

01:48:05.920 --> 01:48:08.280
Ouais? Ouais et toi?

01:48:11.680 --> 01:48:14.040
Non j'peux pas je suis
vraiment cassée.

01:48:14.080 --> 01:48:18.200
Non je voudrais bien mais
je suis vraiment cassée.

01:48:18.240 --> 01:48:21.360
Quais m'en plus j'ai rien
à m'foutre sur le cul.

01:48:21.400 --> 01:48:23.640
V ous bouffez a quelle heure?

01:48:23.680 --> 01:48:25.760
Ah, laisse tomber ouf.

01:48:27.560 --> 01:48:29.440
C'est wrai?

01:48:29.480 --> 01:48:31.960
Ah, c'est cool de I'avoir
invite pour moi.

01:48:38.680 --> 01:48:41.520
Moi remarque j'sais pas
je me le ferai bien quandmeme.

01:48:50.000 --> 01:48:51.120
Ouais?

01:48:52.520 --> 01:48:54.440
Ah, ça doit etre beau.

01:48:55.880 --> 01:48:57.960
Ouais, tu me la passeras?

01:48:59.400 --> 01:49:00.520
Ouais?

01:49:04.280 --> 01:49:05.400
Ouais.

01:49:15.000 --> 01:49:15.920
That was great. Thank you.

01:49:16.480 --> 01:49:18.800
You didn't know
I could cook, did you?

01:49:18.840 --> 01:49:20.480
Thought I could
only shake a leg, huh?

01:49:20.520 --> 01:49:22.920
- You shake a leg real good.
- Better than I cook?

01:49:22.960 --> 01:49:26.040
Sure... Well, I mean, um, no.

01:49:26.080 --> 01:49:28.960
You cook real good,
but you could dance even better.

01:49:28.960 --> 01:49:30.000
You don't work at it.

01:49:30.080 --> 01:49:31.160
What's the point?

01:49:31.160 --> 01:49:32.560
I could never dance
as good as you.

01:49:32.600 --> 01:49:33.680
Sure, you could.

01:49:33.720 --> 01:49:35.800
Come on. You're special.

01:49:35.800 --> 01:49:37.560
Isn't he special, Tiger?

01:49:39.040 --> 01:49:40.120
Absolutely.

01:49:40.160 --> 01:49:42.840
You see?
He loves to watch you dance.

01:49:42.880 --> 01:49:44.280
He thinks you're gorgeous.

01:49:44.320 --> 01:49:46.000
Right, Tiger?

01:49:46.040 --> 01:49:47.120
Right.

01:49:47.160 --> 01:49:49.240
How about that?
Look at that.

01:49:49.280 --> 01:49:51.960
Get a load of that.
Come on.

01:49:52.000 --> 01:49:53.880
Hey, Mims, you're crazy.

01:49:53.920 --> 01:49:55.000
Come on.

01:49:56.800 --> 01:49:58.680
Isn't that something?

01:49:58.720 --> 01:50:01.800
And he's not gay, either.
That's very rare.

01:50:01.840 --> 01:50:04.120
Show him your extension.

01:50:04.160 --> 01:50:05.280
Come on.

01:50:10.640 --> 01:50:12.800
How about that, Tiger?

01:50:12.840 --> 01:50:14.720
You should try it sometime.

01:50:14.760 --> 01:50:18.640
Come on, Basil.
Dance a little for Oscar.

01:50:18.720 --> 01:50:21.240
- I don't know. I ate too much.
- Come on.

01:50:21.280 --> 01:50:25.040
The poor baby gets so little fun
out of life these days.

01:50:25.880 --> 01:50:27.720
No entertainment at all.

01:50:29.680 --> 01:50:30.800
Well?

01:50:40.920 --> 01:50:42.800
Come on! Don't stop!

01:50:55.200 --> 01:50:57.520
Dance! Dance!

01:52:43.120 --> 01:52:47.440
I'd grown accustomed
to being only half a man...

01:52:47.480 --> 01:52:52.240
but that night,
I really hit rock bottom.

01:52:52.600 --> 01:52:55.440
It was a kind of catharsis,
I guess.

01:52:55.480 --> 01:52:57.760
We both knew
we'd never rediscover...

01:52:57.800 --> 01:53:01.080
the same extremes
of passion and cruelty...

01:53:01.120 --> 01:53:02.520
with another living soul.

01:53:02.560 --> 01:53:04.000
Monsieur Oscar Benton...

01:53:04.040 --> 01:53:06.200
consentez-vous
a prendre pour espouse...

01:53:06.240 --> 01:53:08.360
Mademoiselle Micheline Bouvier?

01:53:09.320 --> 01:53:10.680
Mademoiselle
Micheline Bouvier...

01:53:10.720 --> 01:53:12.640
consentez-vous a prendre
pour epoux...

01:53:12.640 --> 01:53:14.040
Monsieur Oscar Benton?

01:53:15.240 --> 01:53:17.120
Conformement a la loi
je vous declare unis...

01:53:17.160 --> 01:53:18.680
par les liens du mariage.

01:53:18.720 --> 01:53:22.680
We were like the survivors
of a catastrophe so terrible...

01:53:22.720 --> 01:53:24.840
it formed a bond between us...

01:53:24.880 --> 01:53:27.880
shared by no one else
in the world.

01:53:47.680 --> 01:53:50.240
So the relationship
had come full circle.

01:53:50.280 --> 01:53:52.200
We'd reached a plateau.

01:53:53.360 --> 01:53:57.800
The dust has settled since then,
but I live in constant dread.

01:53:57.840 --> 01:54:00.600
I'm forever afraid of losing
what's left of her heart...

01:54:00.640 --> 01:54:02.200
to some lucky bastard.

01:54:06.080 --> 01:54:08.160
It feels strange
to be confessing this...

01:54:08.200 --> 01:54:10.640
to someone who's hoping
he'll be the one.

01:54:10.720 --> 01:54:12.120
Now don't deny it.

01:54:12.160 --> 01:54:15.080
There's only room in this cabin
for one hypocrite.

01:54:17.680 --> 01:54:21.160
If you're not going to stay
and have another drink...

01:54:21.200 --> 01:54:23.160
you might as well go.

01:54:23.200 --> 01:54:24.800
There's no more to tell.

01:54:37.760 --> 01:54:40.280
I think I understand you
better now.

01:54:40.280 --> 01:54:41.400
And her?

01:54:44.720 --> 01:54:46.160
Yeah, and her.

01:54:54.280 --> 01:54:56.920
Shit, shit, shit.

01:55:04.280 --> 01:55:05.560
Look...

01:55:06.560 --> 01:55:08.760
Let's be adult about this,
shall we?

01:55:10.680 --> 01:55:13.760
Yeah, adult. That's the word.

01:55:13.800 --> 01:55:16.680
Anything I can do,
you can do better. Feel free.

01:55:16.720 --> 01:55:19.800
I won't object
if you have a little fling...

01:55:19.840 --> 01:55:22.080
with that Italian, for example.

01:57:09.000 --> 01:57:10.600
Taking the plunge at last?

01:57:49.560 --> 01:57:51.520
I think I need a drink.

01:57:53.720 --> 01:57:56.600
I said, I think I need a drink.
Can I get you one?

01:58:04.080 --> 01:58:06.880
Can I have a whiskey, please?
No ice.

01:58:08.160 --> 01:58:10.480
That was some stunt.

01:58:10.520 --> 01:58:14.040
Pretty good for a guy
with two left feet.

01:58:14.080 --> 01:58:16.000
Well, I don't pretend
to be a dancer.

01:58:16.040 --> 01:58:19.400
Just kidding, Nigel.
I'm not so hot myself.

01:58:21.240 --> 01:58:24.560
Will you look at that
Latin lover boy go?

01:58:29.240 --> 01:58:31.520
Watch out. He'll snap her up.

01:58:39.320 --> 01:58:41.560
Almost time.

01:58:41.560 --> 01:58:43.360
Where is that
English rose of yours?

01:58:43.400 --> 01:58:45.240
She'll miss all the fun
if she doesn't hurry up.

01:58:45.280 --> 01:58:48.680
Fiona's not much of a sailor.
She's flat out on her bunk.

01:58:48.720 --> 01:58:51.000
That is a disappointment.

01:58:51.040 --> 01:58:53.400
Yeah, yeah.
Dosed herself on Dramamine.

01:58:53.440 --> 01:58:56.000
Pity. Mimi and I were hoping...

01:58:56.040 --> 01:58:58.360
to crack a bottle of champagne
with you later on...

01:58:58.360 --> 01:59:00.200
the two of you.

01:59:00.240 --> 01:59:02.320
A little farewell get-together
with our special friends.

01:59:02.360 --> 01:59:04.480
All right, folks,
this is it.

01:59:04.520 --> 01:59:05.960
You got something
you want to do this year...

01:59:06.000 --> 01:59:07.240
you'd better hurry up.

01:59:07.280 --> 01:59:09.640
We've got only about
ten seconds left.

01:59:10.600 --> 01:59:12.680
Nine... eight...

01:59:12.720 --> 01:59:14.880
seven... six...

01:59:14.920 --> 01:59:16.960
five... four...

01:59:17.000 --> 01:59:19.040
three... two...

01:59:19.080 --> 01:59:20.440
one!

01:59:36.280 --> 01:59:37.400
Well, baby?

01:59:43.160 --> 01:59:44.960
Happy days, Oscar.

01:59:45.000 --> 01:59:46.120
Sure.

01:59:47.240 --> 01:59:48.640
Happy days.

01:59:58.280 --> 02:00:01.080
Your good health.

02:00:01.120 --> 02:00:03.960
You notice that I do not say,
"Happy New Year."

02:00:04.000 --> 02:00:06.040
To those whose gaze
is focused on eternity...

02:00:06.080 --> 02:00:09.040
one year
is the same as the next.

02:00:09.080 --> 02:00:10.520
You don't say.

02:00:10.520 --> 02:00:12.240
In that case, cheers.

02:00:12.280 --> 02:00:16.200
Deliver a bottle of champagne
to room A-29.

02:00:16.240 --> 02:00:17.480
On my tab.

02:00:17.520 --> 02:00:19.040
Oscar Benton. OK?

02:00:33.760 --> 02:00:35.600
All right,
boys and girls, that'll do.

02:00:35.640 --> 02:00:36.800
Come on, stop that.

02:00:36.840 --> 02:00:39.760
Is this any way to start
a new year?

02:00:39.800 --> 02:00:41.640
Peace! Let's have some peace!

02:00:42.800 --> 02:00:45.200
Shalom! Shalom!

02:00:46.440 --> 02:00:49.360
All right, all right.
Settle down, boys and girls.

02:01:44.880 --> 02:01:46.080
Why?

02:01:47.400 --> 02:01:48.720
I thought...

02:01:48.760 --> 02:01:50.160
You thought what?

02:01:51.160 --> 02:01:53.720
But you said...

02:01:53.760 --> 02:01:55.880
I mean, I know how
your story ends now.

02:01:55.920 --> 02:01:57.400
No, you don't.

02:01:57.440 --> 02:01:59.640
Not yet.

02:01:59.680 --> 02:02:00.920
I think...

02:02:02.480 --> 02:02:05.000
I think I've fallen
in love with you.

02:02:05.040 --> 02:02:10.200
Come on. I'm just a fantasy,
an amusement on a boring voyage.

02:02:11.520 --> 02:02:14.000
You mean it's still just a game?

02:02:14.080 --> 02:02:16.240
Did I ever say it wasn't?

02:02:17.440 --> 02:02:19.640
But...

02:02:19.680 --> 02:02:22.360
I'm truly, sincerely
in love with you.

02:02:22.400 --> 02:02:24.760
That's why you will
never have me.

02:02:29.400 --> 02:02:31.600
You're hurting me terribly.

02:02:31.640 --> 02:02:34.080
The way you're
hurting your wife?

02:02:34.120 --> 02:02:36.560
She doesn't know about us.
She knows nothing.

02:02:36.600 --> 02:02:38.840
She's looking right at us.

02:02:46.760 --> 02:02:48.080
Having a good time?

02:02:48.120 --> 02:02:50.280
Darling, this is wonderful.

02:02:50.320 --> 02:02:52.680
- Yes, isn't it?
- How are you feeling?

02:02:52.720 --> 02:02:55.080
Good as new,
thanks to your ministrations.

02:02:55.120 --> 02:02:56.200
There.

02:02:56.240 --> 02:02:59.360
Now you can make
your New Year's resolutions.

02:02:59.400 --> 02:03:02.280
Do you think it's safe
to drink on an empty stomach?

02:03:02.320 --> 02:03:04.480
Who wants to be safe?

02:03:06.600 --> 02:03:08.400
I'm feeling dangerous tonight.

02:03:08.440 --> 02:03:10.640
That's the spirit, Fiona.

02:03:10.680 --> 02:03:12.240
I knew that your presence...

02:03:12.280 --> 02:03:15.120
would add a little spice
to tonight's proceedings.

02:03:15.160 --> 02:03:17.360
That was a very kind thought
of yours.

02:03:17.400 --> 02:03:18.640
I've never seen my husband...

02:03:18.680 --> 02:03:21.360
in action
with another woman before.

02:03:21.400 --> 02:03:24.240
Oscar had me woken
with a bottle of champagne.

02:03:24.280 --> 02:03:25.680
You call that action?

02:03:25.720 --> 02:03:28.560
I don't think he was
getting anywhere with her.

02:03:31.160 --> 02:03:32.600
It's a shame.

02:05:07.320 --> 02:05:10.720
Maybe I made a mistake
about you, Nigel.

02:05:10.760 --> 02:05:13.560
Maybe your wife
would've been a better bet.

02:05:24.320 --> 02:05:25.640
Come on, stop sulking, man.

02:05:25.680 --> 02:05:29.520
You ought to be glad
they're getting it on so well.

02:05:29.600 --> 02:05:32.880
Come on. Put a funny hat on.
It'll make you feel better.

02:05:32.920 --> 02:05:35.040
Throw some streamers at them.

02:05:41.720 --> 02:05:42.960
Attaboy!

02:05:43.000 --> 02:05:45.360
It's the "Titanic"
all over again!

02:05:45.400 --> 02:05:49.120
Nearer my God to thee

02:05:49.160 --> 02:05:51.960
Nearer to thee

02:06:20.000 --> 02:06:22.120
I know how you feel, Nigel.

02:06:22.160 --> 02:06:24.240
I've been a loser all my life.

02:06:24.280 --> 02:06:25.680
Join the club.

02:06:25.720 --> 02:06:27.440
Don't touch me!

02:06:27.480 --> 02:06:29.840
If you weren't a cripple,
I'd knock your fucking head off.

02:06:29.880 --> 02:06:31.760
Go ahead if it'll help.

02:06:31.800 --> 02:06:33.080
I deserve your hatred.

02:06:33.080 --> 02:06:35.320
I'm abominable. I'm pathetic.

02:06:40.240 --> 02:06:42.120
No, not that way, Nigel.

02:06:42.160 --> 02:06:43.560
Nigel, you better hurry.

02:06:43.600 --> 02:06:46.240
There'll be nothing left
for you.

02:06:51.200 --> 02:06:54.080
Bloody hell!

02:07:58.360 --> 02:07:59.640
Is she here?

02:08:15.240 --> 02:08:20.120
Did you ever see such
an allegory of grace and beauty?

02:08:20.160 --> 02:08:24.040
Two nymphs sleeping off
their amatory exertions.

02:08:26.400 --> 02:08:28.400
You really missed something,
Nigel.

02:08:28.480 --> 02:08:32.240
Fiona was a revelation.

02:08:32.280 --> 02:08:34.560
All fire.

02:08:36.400 --> 02:08:41.080
I doubt if you've ever really
made the most of her.

02:08:42.920 --> 02:08:44.400
Swine!

02:08:44.440 --> 02:08:47.640
Get your goddamn hands off me.

02:08:55.200 --> 02:08:56.880
You prick.

02:09:00.800 --> 02:09:03.760
You don't deserve to hear
the rest of my story.

02:09:03.800 --> 02:09:05.880
My.

02:09:05.920 --> 02:09:07.280
Here, give it.

02:09:07.320 --> 02:09:09.440
Just give me that thing,
all right?

02:09:09.480 --> 02:09:10.920
Otherwise you're going
to hurt somebody.

02:09:10.960 --> 02:09:12.240
Come on, man,
Don't be a bloody fool.

02:09:12.280 --> 02:09:13.800
- Give it to me.
- Hurt somebody?

02:09:17.720 --> 02:09:19.240
Not anymore.

02:09:26.280 --> 02:09:28.760
We were just too greedy, baby.

02:09:30.920 --> 02:09:32.320
That was all.

02:10:10.600 --> 02:10:11.840
Hello, sweetheart.

02:10:11.880 --> 02:10:15.000
My father says to wish you
a Happy New Year.

